EMAIL TYPES BY CATEGORY
ONBOARDING EMAILS
New users series New customers series Key onboarding step reminders New user invites 
RETENTION EMAILS
Upgrade to paid Upgrade to higher plan Ask for review Proactive support offers Product usage reports NPS survey Referral program 
BILLING EMAILS
Switch to annual Failed payment recovery Cancellation survey Upcoming renewal reminders 
USAGE EMAILS
Daily/weekly/monthly summaries Key event notifications Milestone celebrations 
WIN-BACK EMAILS
Expired trials Cancelled customers 
CAMPAIGN EMAILS
Monthly roundup / newsletter Seasonal promotions Product updates Industry news roundup Pricing updates 
For detailed email type reference: See references/email-types.md 
